SETUP
---

1. Get Ruby, Rubygems, and bundler.
sudo apt-get install ruby-full
sudo gem update --system
sudo gem install bundler

2. Install mongodb, if necessary.
sudo apt-get install mongodb

3. Install all the required gems.
bundle install

4. Create or update the database
bundle exec server/db_schema.rb

5. Start up the web server.
bundle exec shotgun config.ru
nohup bundle exec unicorn config.ru > web.log &

6. Start up the chat server.
bundle exec ./chatty_ws.rb
nohup bundle exec server/boot.rb > server.log &
